{"tid":1941049,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"破解用戶數字驟降之謎   中國聯通董事長咁解釋","createTime":"2020-03-24T07:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T16:30:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"eac6f9756f29d84a5000a1316863232a0e0c4013","tid":1941049,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"虎仔 / 馬日山(uniqlo) 2020-03-24 12:24<br />\nwhatsapp sharing button facebook sharing button messenger sharing button telegram sharing button twitter sharing button email sharing button sharethis sharing button<br />\n日前有線電視財經台發現，大陸用戶數字在 2 月大幅下跌，報導一出即時引起網民的議論。有熱心網民製作了大陸三大電訊商用戶增減的統計表，指用戶數量銳減了 1,447 萬多，到底這些消失了的用戶去了哪裡？有網民直指他們轉台到天國移動、天國電信和天國聯通，又有人認為與武漢肺炎影響經濟有關，導致用戶終止服務。<br />\n<br />\n昨日中國聯通董事長王曉初出席 2019 年業績發佈會時，就對用戶人數減少作出官方的解釋。王曉初表示客戶流失並非中國聯通獨有，而是各電訊商都面對的情況，他認為流失的原因或者是源自「雙卡用戶」。由於武漢肺炎疫情的緣故，部份用戶或會在短時間内放棄其中一張電話卡，所以導致客戶數量有所減少。"},{"pid":"15867664fca81f82a41e12f4c306d95cbe6419b6","tid":1941049,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/215500/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4247%2F215500%2F1%2F&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ3za4IX%2BHJq2V8VgSm%2B5QfQ%3D&h=167fc0b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4247/215500/1/</a>"},{"pid":"e5bc5f87e191f87d5c2934069e3f146cd9300822","tid":1941049,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c91002375ff43ae5aa36a6a48705cd2d1e7613","tid":1941049,"uid":16034,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T07:34:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大陸實名登記架嘛 係雙卡你點唔知 咩撚野可能者"},